    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a suitable project or budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are currently functional, but you should expect some mechanical wear consistent with its age, including minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose. The exterior shows its history with several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some fading in the paint. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows significant wear on the upholstery and some non-essential electronic features may be temperamental. It is a reliable runner for now, but it will likely need professional servicing in the near future to stay on the road.",
