    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years, so it's ready for many more miles. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road with its next owner. It runs like a dream and looks even better in person! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
