      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is managed by double VANOS, providing a broad torque curve. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a rear subframe reinforcement kit to address known chassis fatigue points. Equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the handling remains sharp thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, ensuring the visceral driving experience these M-cars are known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
