      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. This car features a lustrous exterior finish with only minor signs of road use, complemented by a smoke-free interior that remains remarkably crisp. The leather upholstery shows minimal wear, and every dashboard control functions as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key; it has benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule, including a recent fluid service and a fresh set of premium tires. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission offers precise, confident shifts. Whether you\u2019re commuting or taking a weekend trip, this car offers a refined driving experience that reflects its careful ownership history. Includes complete service records and two sets of keys.",
